            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d74074-Hd1e108">Rubrica 8</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d74074-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De credito et debito maxime vsurario</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d74074-d1e114">
              De credito et debito et
              vsurariorum supra de prehibitione
              eius capitulum
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d74074-d1e121">
              <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d74074-Rd1e122">SAlomon
              <lb ed="#C"/>prouerbiis capitulo
              <lb ed="#C"/>22</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d74074-Qd1e131">qui accipit mutuum seruus est feneran<lb ed="#C" break="no"/>tis </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d74074-d1e137">
              ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d74074-Rd1e137">Lex auten titulo de he et falc § dudum
              <lb ed="#C"/>Adiecto</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d74074-Qd1e141">debitor creditorem veretur et me<lb ed="#C" break="no"/>tuit</quote> 
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d74074-d1e150">
              ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d74074-Rd1e153">Bertrandus yconomica capitulo XVIII</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d74074-Qd1e154">Melius est par<lb ed="#C" break="no"/>tem 
              patrimonii uendere quam vsuris te subi<lb ed="#C" break="no"/>cere 
              ¶ Quid est usura uenenum paranti<lb ed="#C" break="no"/>um 
              legalis latro perdicans quid intendit</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d74074-d1e162">
              [omitted]
            </p>
